msg.text: (garry:Er boss I've done a small modification to a cement mixer ) (foreman:Garry what have you made this time? ) (garry:A cannon! A cement mixer that fires cannon balls! ) (garry:It's easy to use: Just position the cannon, find a good angle and hold down the mouse button till you have enough power!) (foreman:Oh dear, oh dear. Try to destroy JUST the building this time! And keep away from my van!!)
